Title: AN ACT CHANGING THE NAME OF THE BARRIO OF BALUG0. MUNICIPALITY OF GUINAYANGAN, PROVINCE OF TAYABAS, TO THAT OF LAUREL.
Data:
[ Commonwealth Act No. 579, June 08, 1940 ]
AN ACT CHANGING THE NAME OF THE BARRIO OF BALUG0. MUNICIPALITY OF GUINAYANGAN, PROVINCE OF TAYABAS, TO THAT OF LAUREL.
Be it enacted by the National Assembly of the Philippines:
Section 1. The name of the barrio of Balugo of the Municipality of Guinayangan, Province of Tayabas, is changed to that of Laurel.ℒαwρhi৷
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Enacted, without Executive approval, June 8, 1940.
